{"title":"诗人将叩响黎明的门环","authors":["宋丹"],"dates":[{"year":1988,"month":9,"day":23}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"诗人将叩响黎明的门环"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宋丹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜色"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"砌成的墙"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高得令人压抑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"即使是"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"商禽的长颈鹿①"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也无法企及"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而那扇"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唯一的圆窗上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"依稀有相思的泪痕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"虽然"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"盛开的桂花"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"温馨了古老的传奇"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但李白床前的霜色"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"至今还在令游子的梦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"凝重如铁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"虽然"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无形的黑墙上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"已经凿满星星的洞孔"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但历史的阴影"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"并没有被阳光漂白"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"以至使"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最普通的家人团聚"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"竟成为一种奢望"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天涯海角"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"空对一颗愈望愈渴的黄梅"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欲哭无泪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而今宵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"昆明湖的翡翠杯里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"斟满醉人的笑语"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"船桨拍打云影"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"溅起透明的诗韵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"画舫如黄鹤"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从排云殿前起飞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了永恒的团圆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每一只"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"握笔的手"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都渴望在辉煌的终点"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叩响那枚"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黎明的门环……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"①商禽：台湾著名现代派诗人。《长颈鹿》系其名作。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"注：北京、台湾部分诗人将于明天在颐和园举行中秋诗会。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}